---
title: Smart Spicy Salmon and Poblano Stew with Lemon-Chili Couscous
description: Hearty deliciousness is the name of the game with this stew. Load up each spoonful with tender salmon, savoury tomato broth and spicy lemon-parsley couscous for an unforgettable flavour bomb in every bite!

